<plot>The Klingons, the classic Star Trek race of warriors, are running out of resources. The only way to continue the proud race, they must conquer vast areas of resource-rich space and battle their foes. General Chang (Christopher Plummer) convinces Chancellor Gorkon (David Warner) to build a battle academy to defeat their long time foe, The United Federation of Planets. You play as a Klingon Warrior training to command a warship, while the Klingons face Civil War, Planetary Conquest, countless skirmishes, and even self-annihilation.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?513651</url></doc>
